snippet.title: Kings Bounty (1990) gameplay
snippet.description: Kings Bounty, one of my first game. It has much to offer even after so time. Its game from 1990 and started new era of gaming, for example famous heroes of might and magic was inspired by this game. You can download this game here for free http://www.gamesforyou.ic.cz/hry/bounty.html
